{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-article-js","path":"/blog/importance-cyber-security-motivus","result":{"data":{"sanityPost":{"title":"Importance of Cyber Security in Motivus","_rawContent":[{"_key":"1019fd45b752","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"da36234e3036","_type":"span","marks":["strong"],"text":"Because we are completely aware of the importance of cyber security and data privacy in the modern age, the following article will explain the security measures that the Motivus Framework employs to ensure that your device, and your data, is perfectly safe."}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"42ea0a5d81d3","_type":"codepen","variant":"body1"},{"_key":"eca116136506","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"cfb67f9915330","_type":"span","marks":["strong"],"text":"Motivus runs in a safe, sandboxed execution environment."}],"markDefs":[],"style":"h3"},{"_key":"8026b4757d2f","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"245f3b91c8da","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":""}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"a2ebde2245ee","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"3aa6026c773a0","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"A sandboxed environment is an effective way to improve your device’s security. It is designed to prevent threats by isolating apps from each other."}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"cbe63c8ddff9","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"1e51a41ae54c","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":""}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"70d4d2fbfdaf","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"a07f3ae6ec210","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"Because sandboxing keeps apps relegated to isolated test environments, these won’t infect or cause damage to the host machine or operating system."}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"0965f6c47f19","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"4a3119e4a18b","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":""}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"e69dc878e86a","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"ca7dac3c06260","_type":"span","marks":["strong"],"text":"Motivus and WebAssembly’s Nanoprocesses"}],"markDefs":[{"_key":"41e83ca90524","_type":"link","href":"https://webassembly.org/docs/security/"}],"style":"h3"},{"_key":"e6a9c2bda2bb","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"53db6187790c","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":""}],"markDefs":[{"_key":"41e83ca90524","_type":"link","href":"https://webassembly.org/docs/security/"}],"style":"h3"},{"_key":"3f4032f1d30c","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"7e2da4227660","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"Motivus is hosted on WebAssembly, where they have an implemented security model that has two important goals. As "},{"_key":"d5301445630e1","_type":"span","marks":["41e83ca90524"],"text":"stated on the official WebAssembly site"},{"_key":"d5301445630e2","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":":"}],"markDefs":[{"_key":"41e83ca90524","_type":"link","href":"https://webassembly.org/docs/security/"}],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"50e455290ada","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"fdca9b634e67","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":""}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"fa661471dbfb","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"6657057609c50","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"(1) Protect users from buggy or malicious modules, and (2) provide developers with useful primitives and mitigations for developing safe applications, within the constraints of (1)."}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"b97c2a5a72d9","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"92513f56acd2","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":""}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"d8b4122995f9","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"0e7f8e6b79040","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"For user’s security, each WebAssembly module executes within a sandboxed environment separated from the host runtime using fault isolation techniques. This implies:"}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"8a594e4861c5","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"8b905021116f","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":""}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"cba10c637167","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"32268b8fba350","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"Applications execute independently, and can’t escape the sandbox without going through appropriate APIs."}],"level":1,"listItem":"bullet","markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"dc76ac87052e","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"c85866be974c0","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"Applications generally execute deterministically "},{"_key":"c85866be974c1","_type":"span","marks":["3b847e4469e0"],"text":"with limited exceptions"},{"_key":"c85866be974c2","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"."}],"level":1,"listItem":"bullet","markDefs":[{"_key":"3b847e4469e0","_type":"link","href":"https://webassembly.org/docs/nondeterminism/"}],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"72605118b157","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"7cb9fe8a5706","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":""}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"fa4ee8218bfd","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"25ae7cd3b57f0","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"WebAssembly and other companies have also created the "},{"_key":"25ae7cd3b57f1","_type":"span","marks":["0085b747bac7"],"text":"Bytecode Alliance"},{"_key":"25ae7cd3b57f2","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":", where they are seeking to achieve full security of WebAssembly through a system called Nanoprocesses."}],"markDefs":[{"_key":"0085b747bac7","_type":"link","href":"https://hacks.mozilla.org/2019/11/announcing-the-bytecode-alliance/"}],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"3ba833e87697","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"01026b4f817e","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":""}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"7f43bc38da3c","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"f909aed371770","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"The essence of the problem is the access that malicious code has when it spots vulnerabilities in the application’s code. This is why restricting access is the way to achieve security."}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"6c3d342581b4","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"c41d9da60f8b0","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":""}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"2ba31dbdf621","_type":"image","asset":{"_id":"image-0bed1c22b10fc6db1261df5a8f91d01a2b2f1a3f-1308x901-png","_type":"sanity.imageAsset","_rev":"vy79jLBbbaaSbrT5Ov4Oo2","_createdAt":"2021-01-12T18:49:00Z","_updatedAt":"2021-01-12T18:49:00Z","assetId":"0bed1c22b10fc6db1261df5a8f91d01a2b2f1a3f","extension":"png","metadata":{"_type":"sanity.imageMetadata","dimensions":{"_type":"sanity.imageDimensions","aspectRatio":1.4517203107658159,"height":901,"width":1308},"hasAlpha":true,"isOpaque":true,"lqip":"data:image/png;base64,","palette":{"_type":"sanity.imagePalette","darkMuted":{"_type":"sanity.imagePaletteSwatch","background":"#345670","foreground":"#fff","population":0.14,"title":"#fff"},"darkVibrant":{"_type":"sanity.imagePaletteSwatch","background":"#135b99","foreground":"#fff","population":1.86,"title":"#fff"},"dominant":{"_type":"sanity.imagePaletteSwatch","background":"#135b99","foreground":"#fff","population":1.86,"title":"#fff"},"lightMuted":{"_type":"sanity.imagePaletteSwatch","background":"#95aec3","foreground":"#000","population":1.44,"title":"#fff"},"lightVibrant":{"_type":"sanity.imagePaletteSwatch","background":"#6ec1fb","foreground":"#000","population":0.18,"title":"#fff"},"muted":{"_type":"sanity.imagePaletteSwatch","background":"#648fae","foreground":"#fff","population":0.9,"title":"#fff"},"vibrant":{"_type":"sanity.imagePaletteSwatch","background":"#1184e1","foreground":"#fff","population":0.09,"title":"#fff"}}},"mimeType":"image/png","originalFilename":"05-01-protection-initial.png","path":"images/2g00hyzc/production/0bed1c22b10fc6db1261df5a8f91d01a2b2f1a3f-1308x901.png","sha1hash":"0bed1c22b10fc6db1261df5a8f91d01a2b2f1a3f","size":143143,"uploadId":"YIT7bE6Mcy51ci61DteKzoqdmQsJVsjY","url":"https://cdn.sanity.io/images/2g00hyzc/production/0bed1c22b10fc6db1261df5a8f91d01a2b2f1a3f-1308x901.png","id":"image-0bed1c22b10fc6db1261df5a8f91d01a2b2f1a3f-1308x901-png","parent":null,"children":[],"internal":{"type":"SanityImageAsset","contentDigest":"f878fcfb5a385502e1b50d6eabb41941","counter":68,"owner":"gatsby-source-sanity"}}},{"_key":"8b1c0b02df3e","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"c80327dfa7980","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"Lin Clark’s cartoons show how WebAssembly employs data security. Read more about it on the article "},{"_key":"c80327dfa7981","_type":"span","marks":["01538542ee36"],"text":"Building a secure by default, composable future for WebAssembly"},{"_key":"c80327dfa7982","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"."}],"markDefs":[{"_key":"01538542ee36","_type":"link","href":"https://hacks.mozilla.org/2019/11/announcing-the-bytecode-alliance/"}],"style":"blockquote"},{"_key":"5e8340a3bd13","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"2ff658c9bf1d","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":""}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"4ae3763ef854","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"d6134a4cd3040","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"For example, in order for malicious modules to carry out an attack, it needs to access the resources and APIs that it shouldn’t have permission to go into."}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"58a5b29f36a6","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"042b75451832","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":""}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"ea71481e8792","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"ab6c543f7e140","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"WebAssembly isolates the different modules from each other and gives them fine-grained permissions to particular parts of the file system and other resources, and also fine grained permissions for different system calls. All of this makes it easy to see when it’s asking to do things it shouldn’t."}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"2a710d5105cf","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"f868f8d0ea5c","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":""}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"f785e5659393","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"2b03d39347340","_type":"span","marks":["strong"],"text":"Browser Security for extra safety"}],"markDefs":[],"style":"h3"},{"_key":"49f905ce032c","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"32804289c4e8","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":""}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"8bd05a32353f","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"90ed9d4139190","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"Most web browsers default settings are designed to be secure when it comes to malware infections. For example, Firefox detects untrusted content and then runs it in a sandboxed low-rights environment. It does this so that if the code happens to compromise security, it won’t have access to full system functionality and resources."}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"b293bdae7427","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"9e5ea487b0770","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"Sandboxing technology is run on all major browsers of today, including Chrome and Microsoft Edge. This will secure your computer from infections, however, it won’t necessarily prevent browsers from accessing data which they will later use for advertisement purposes."}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"e9461c2b4895","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"05506cfc72820","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"If you are concerned about your data being used for advertisement purposes, then we recommend you visit Restore Privacy’s recommendations for the "},{"_key":"05506cfc72821","_type":"span","marks":["62d0b364fc81"],"text":"7 most secure browsers that protect your privacy"},{"_key":"05506cfc72822","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":". On the top of the list you will find browsers like Firefox and Brave, which with certain tweaks on their settings allow for an absolute private browsing experience."}],"markDefs":[{"_key":"62d0b364fc81","_type":"link","href":"https://restoreprivacy.com/browser/secure/"}],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"c4876ee53c1f","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"5f224ab42e89","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":""}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"d1289a2d3457","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"33774fa94e100","_type":"span","marks":["strong"],"text":"HTTPS Encryption in Motivus"}],"markDefs":[],"style":"h3"},{"_key":"52f265948f42","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"85b5e69e13490","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":""}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"b6a3011eb388","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"e98bc5a792b60","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"See that lock icon on the tip left of your browser’s address bar? That means that the website you’re in has increased security. You will spot this icon on every major website where users transmit sensitive data, like when you’re logged into your bank account on your bank’s website or even your email service. Motivus also exists on HTTPS encryption."}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"e89f1969a84b","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"c4a6ba4318f30","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":""}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"7e879f51ad55","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"489a70943f6f0","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"Hypertext transfer protocol secure (HTTPS) is the secure version of "},{"_key":"489a70943f6f1","_type":"span","marks":["83b07968752b"],"text":"HTTP"},{"_key":"489a70943f6f2","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":". This is the primary protocol used to send data between a web browser and a website. The encryption in HTTPS was created in order to increase the security of data transfers. HTTPS is encrypted in order to increase security of data transfer. This is particularly important when users transmit sensitive data, such as by logging into a bank account, email service, or health insurance provider."}],"markDefs":[{"_key":"83b07968752b","_type":"link","href":"https://www.cloudflare.com/learning/ddos/glossary/hypertext-transfer-protocol-http/"}],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"c640df9e44cb","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"8a8580b8638f","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":""}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"7b130513fa74","_type":"codepen"},{"_key":"20a1d9920531","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"963b28be3ead0","_type":"span","marks":["strong"],"text":"Any questions about Cyber Security in the Motivus Framework? Please use the contact form on our main menu to reach out."}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"5c856104a2e1","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"7b9f89d697e40","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"\n"}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"}],"abstract":"This article will explain the security measures that the Motivus Framework employs to ensure that your device, and your data, is perfectly safe.","image":{"asset":{"fixed":{"base64":"data:image/jpeg;base64,","width":960,"height":634,"src":"https://cdn.sanity.io/images/2g00hyzc/production/14f20006f165ce23453d6be55c4df92d6afccce3-900x594.jpg","srcSet":"https://cdn.sanity.io/images/2g00hyzc/production/14f20006f165ce23453d6be55c4df92d6afccce3-900x594.jpg 1x","srcWebp":"https://cdn.sanity.io/images/2g00hyzc/production/14f20006f165ce23453d6be55c4df92d6afccce3-900x594.jpg?fm=webp","srcSetWebp":"https://cdn.sanity.io/images/2g00hyzc/production/14f20006f165ce23453d6be55c4df92d6afccce3-900x594.jpg?fm=webp 1x"}}},"author":{"id":"-e4aaf93f-a2c3-596e-8216-1183d34c6157","name":"Rodrigo Inostroza"},"publishedAt":"2021-01-12T08:00:00.000Z"}},"pageContext":{"id":"-2a10154a-ee47-5916-99f6-b4abeaa761a8"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3649515864","63159454"]}